title: Seen Through Glass
description: We're joined by Sam (@SeenThruGlass) the man behind the Seen Through Glass YouTube channel. Sam shares a bit about his extended stay here in the states, what it's like producing a YouTube channel from the UK among myriad other topics.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
